reviews.review_text:
My First Show This was my first Dead show. I came in a school bus full of hippies from Ann Arbor.  Was in the last row of the first section of floor seats and was shocked that the audience stood the whole show.

The show was great fun, the 12 hour bus ride home did teach me: Don't drop acid if you're driving the bus back home.

The recording quality of this copy is ok, there are many other shows that have better recordings.
